<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8' standalone='no'?>
<doxygen xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="compound.xsd" version="1.14.0" xml:lang="en-US">
  <compounddef id="UPTIMES" kind="page">
    <compoundname>UPTIMES</compoundname>
    <title>UPTIME$ Function</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">UPTIME$</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Returns the system <bold>uptime as a human-readable string</bold>.</para>
<para>The value represents how long the system has been running since it was started, formatted into days, hours, minutes, and seconds.</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<sect1 id="UPTIMES_1examples-130_1s1"><sect2 id="UPTIMES_1examples-130_1s2"><sect3 id="UPTIMES_1examples-130">
<title>Examples</title><para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">REM<sp/>Print<sp/>formatted<sp/>uptime</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;Uptime:<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>UPTIME$</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">REM<sp/>Include<sp/>uptime<sp/>in<sp/>a<sp/>status<sp/>message</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;System<sp/>has<sp/>been<sp/>running<sp/>for<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>UPTIME$</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">REM<sp/>Simple<sp/>log<sp/>output</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;[&quot;;<sp/>UPTIME$;<sp/>&quot;]<sp/>System<sp/>ready&quot;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect3></sect2></sect1>
<sect1 id="UPTIMES_1notes-127_1s1"><sect2 id="UPTIMES_1notes-127_1s2"><sect3 id="UPTIMES_1notes-127">
<title>Notes</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Returns a string such as <bold>&quot;0 days, 6 hours, 5 mins 23 secs&quot;</bold>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Intended for display purposes rather than timing.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>For numeric timing or comparisons, use <ref refid="UPSECS" kindref="compound">UPSECS</ref> or <ref refid="TICKS" kindref="compound">TICKS</ref>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ref refid="UPSECS" kindref="compound">UPSECS</ref> · <ref refid="TICKS" kindref="compound">TICKS</ref> </para>
</sect3></sect2></sect1>
    </detaileddescription>
